title: LoLLauncher
body:
Any fixes? I look up how but all I see is people posting this log error but no one ever tell them how to fix it 
ERROR| Riot::RADS::Patching::RetrieveReleaseListing: C:/jenkins/workspace/rads-code-win-release/code/Solutions/RiotRADS/Source/RADS/Patching/Networking/ClientServer/RemoteFileServerCommon.cpp(63): Failed to create version number from release listing entry "

replies.body: At a glance, it seems like your computer is blocking the game from scanning files.  As a first step, I suggest going over our [Permissions ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions)guide for a fix.  If your issue persists, please submit this log to our tech team by[ submitting a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
So no one know how to fix this? rip me
